item.title: HELP? [delta]
item.dc:creator: @Tutorial Tutorial
item.description:
@Tutorial wrote:

The client read errors are most caused because the sprites it shows are either missing or corrupted. The reason you can’t connect to your server is most likely being caused by the fact that you port forwarded incorrectly.
